    <tu tuid="shijing__song-chengong-003__001__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
      <prop type="x-section-id">song-chengong-003</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·臣工之什·003.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">振鷺.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>振鷺于飛，于彼西雝。我客戾止，亦有斯容。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>A flock of egrets is flying,
About the marsh there in the west.
My visitors came,
With an (elegant) carriage like those birds.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__song-chengong-003__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
      <prop type="x-section-id">song-chengong-003</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·臣工之什·003.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">振鷺.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>在彼無惡，在此無斁。庶幾夙夜，以永終譽。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>There, (in their states), not disliked,
Here, (in Kâu), never tired of;—
They
are sure, day and night,
To perpetuate their fame.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
